OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FClear spells, dry east at first
OL,6,Fthen outbreaks of locally heavy rain
OL,7,Fin the west soon spreads east. This
OL,8,Frain will clear to bright spells and
OL,9,Fscattered showers in the afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FBright or clear spells with
OL,12,Fshowery rain west at first becoming
OL,13,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain west,
OL,14,Fsome heavy, from just after midnight.
OL,15,
OL,16,CFriday:FCloudy with outbreaks of
OL,17,Foccasionally heavy rain becoming drier
OL,18,Fwith bright spells from the mid-
OL,19,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
