OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRain
OL,6,Fclears north Saturday morning to leave
OL,7,Fthe afternoon and Sunday dry and
OL,8,Fbright. A band of cloud and outbreaks
OL,9,Fof rain, heavy at times, pass east
OL,10,FMonday morning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
